<section>
Basic Information
</section>

<section>
<h3>Graphs can encode connections</h3>
<p>A graph $\Gamma$ consists of:</p>
<ul> 
<li>A set $V(\Gamma)$ of vertices (things)</li>
<li>A set $E(\Gamma)$ of edges (connections)</li>
</ul>
<p>Each edge $e\in E(\Gamma)$ connects two vertices in  $V(\Gamma)$.</p>



</section>






